{"tid":1739402,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"衷心感謝poly留守到今晚既FA","createTime":"2019-11-19T14:43:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T16:55:08.000Z","uid":233449,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c3365743010c83360dda8eac922076b0621af84d","tid":1739402,"uid":233449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T14:43:06.000Z","msg":"所有手足<br />\n所有香港人<br />\n都好感謝你地呢幾日無條件既付出"},{"pid":"902811e0190e0aea5ea1450c99557e8ac997e29d","tid":1739402,"uid":233449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T14:46:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"be1bbcd4d6b95ef384fe56565bfaf6db3611e109","tid":1739402,"uid":248394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T14:46:48.000Z","msg":"多謝你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"832faaf1742260979cfe7468d903c430fdf21efa","tid":1739402,"uid":33904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T16:26:43.000Z","msg":"對唔住&hellip;<br />\n我地FA心理上同體力上好多已經崩潰&hellip;<br />\n一開始我地煲大出聲明係想死守最後<br />\n但我帶唔贏風向<br />\n最後變左拉隊走<br />\n<br />\n對唔住 各位留守既手足<br />\n我地一路諗住比其他手足行暗道走先<br />\n然後我地一路睇住偷走失敗<br />\n周身傷哂既手足<br />\n我地好多人真係頂唔順&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n我自己係入面三日通頂，加埋訓唔多過兩三粒鐘，就算自己想留，拉唔到多人陪自己，都係唔夠膽自己留，焗住要一齊走&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n加上收到風話poly唔會清場，但會封鎖到12月，食物食水呢兩日都開始唔夠，<br />\n我地將食物食水留比決定匿埋既你地，<br />\n希望多少幫到你地。"},{"pid":"7ff56375a9f8270cda862b299774858cf564d014","tid":1739402,"uid":233449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T16:55:08.000Z","msg":"推"}]}